CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in New Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, April 1, 1967, pg. 13 reads: "Summer Preview - Shelia Howell, Gwendolyn Bridgeforth and Gloria Williams gave viewers a preview of summer in bathing suits that they modeled at the Fashion Show given by Cyrene Chapter 9, OES, PHA, at the Homewood YMCA on Palm Sunday. - All Harris photos."
TitMainTitle: Shelia Howell, Gwendolyn Bridgeforth, and Gloria Williams modeling swim wear for Fashion Show given by Cyrene Chapter 9, OES, PHA, at Homewood YMCA
